    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/3639413f9e42c6a7205c601124cd2884.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《戴森球计划》是一款融合了太空、自动化工厂、冒险、探索等元素的科幻题材沙盒建造类游戏。在未来，人类创造了超级计算机——“主脑”，以期待利用其强大的计算能力来进一步扩大虚拟世界的运用。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/7fad1458f27b7dd52da5117da11e2c7c.poster.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/7fad1458f27b7dd52da5117da11e2c7c.webm?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将作为空间管理联盟COSMO的工程师，开启的一项代号为“戴森球计划”的项目——建造戴森球，以充分利用恒星的光辉，为“主脑”提供持续稳定的能量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/c772b456be7f39fee77fe9e72909856b.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=122 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机生成的星图，每一局都是独一无二的宇宙。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更加微观的建造戴森球，从一个零件开始构架。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗，建造防御建筑，抵御敌人来袭，或强化自身直接来一场血战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索千变万化的宇宙生态，中子星、白矮星、红巨星，甚至黑洞。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不止于地表的自动化生产流水线，跨越星系运输物资。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种可自主定制的设定，打造属于你自己的戴森球计划。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >球形地表，完美表现在一颗星球之上完成建设的特色。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蓝图功能，保存重要的规划，省去重复的操作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机甲自定义，用你的聪明才智创造出独一无二的设计，带着它遨游星海。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/438bbbeec9591a8345784cd61a638d93.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要建设戴森球，你需要通过由简入繁的自动化设计，充分利用自动化设施达来到物资的稳定产出。将资源通过传送带连通于各个建筑之间，将原材料送至加工设施，再将产物输送往下一个设施。从简单的流水线设计，逐步发展至产物丰富的大工厂的规划。利用你的产出，推动科技进步，达成建造戴森球的必要条件。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/f1e2a41974156fb06380f33b705096a4.poster.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/f1e2a41974156fb06380f33b705096a4.webm?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/f1e2a41974156fb06380f33b705096a4.mp4?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在建造过程中建筑会自动吸附网格，铺设流水线时可以利用建筑网格吸附功能自动对齐建筑，大大提高建造效率，形成大规模的自动化流水线。戴森球的建设将有赖于庞大而高效的工厂。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/90f03b219d0280eb1bda415c8a8ed193.poster.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/90f03b219d0280eb1bda415c8a8ed193.webm?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/90f03b219d0280eb1bda415c8a8ed193.mp4?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >便捷的蓝图科技，保存你的重要规划。使用蓝图功能，将工厂设计保存为蓝图，在其他位置直接部署，省去重复操作的烦恼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/b5e8e06956d99a8dbbaa176555ecd77b.poster.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/b5e8e06956d99a8dbbaa176555ecd77b.webm?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/b5e8e06956d99a8dbbaa176555ecd77b.mp4?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/b3f7521ee93d03e679b1f3e66921294e.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可在多个轨道上修建戴森壳，每层戴森壳都可以由你定制。在戴森壳上连接各个节点，画出你想要的图案，每一个戴森球都是独属于你的作品。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/520aea88e04387761bb3269b31e4e2ce.poster.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/520aea88e04387761bb3269b31e4e2ce.webm?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/520aea88e04387761bb3269b31e4e2ce.mp4?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/0b167ecc9f9231d2baa14cfe7341b01e.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一个星球都将具有独特的矿物分布和生态特征，每一次进入游戏都可以体验到随机生成全新的星图，地形和矿藏也会随之变化。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/5dd5d08c799a2edc982204246fbea660.poster.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/5dd5d08c799a2edc982204246fbea660.webm?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/5dd5d08c799a2edc982204246fbea660.mp4?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各式各样的星球和天象，星球不会在太空中孤独悬浮。每一个星系内的每一颗星球，都拥有自己轨道，有着受恒星引力影响的公转自转，和受其光芒影响的晦明变化。除此之外，还有独特的中子星、白矮星、红巨星，甚至黑洞，在这个宇宙中等待你的见证。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/dd3127b666989ff4192ff0b73ae16518.poster.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/dd3127b666989ff4192ff0b73ae16518.webm?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/dd3127b666989ff4192ff0b73ae16518.mp4?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/5ea94598606ddcb92a6d93f4d553a814.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个星球的矿产或许不足以实现如此庞大的计划，而其他星球的丰富资源和珍奇也可以为你所用。建设跨越地表运输的限制，组建你的星际运输航线。用运输船队将星球之间串联，利用各个星球的独特资源，为工厂提供源源不断的原料。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/8c97178d3a51bbd62749b77c3e513b9a.poster.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/8c97178d3a51bbd62749b77c3e513b9a.webm?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/8c97178d3a51bbd62749b77c3e513b9a.mp4?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/011abb2a61da2441b9cb43f648f20037.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不仅可以为伊卡洛斯涂上喜欢的颜色，还可以定制每一个部位，打造你心目中属于未来的轻型工业机甲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/11b4f5c2440fd91fe996f68402ef3d8f.poster.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/11b4f5c2440fd91fe996f68402ef3d8f.webm?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/11b4f5c2440fd91fe996f68402ef3d8f.mp4?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/86fa6d1bcfbe62d1cae6fc1c3548f771.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑雾已经来临，它们将为你的工厂建设带来无数挑战。在“黑雾崛起”中，除了继续执行构建戴森球的目标，你还要兼顾防御自己的工厂。黑雾会尽一切可能阻止你实施“戴森球计划”，连伊卡洛斯也是它们进攻的目标，做好准备！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/248fdb4904fccc8f6ef654c7ba718287.poster.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/248fdb4904fccc8f6ef654c7ba718287.webm?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/248fdb4904fccc8f6ef654c7ba718287.mp4?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑雾的集群数量众多，不要指望轻型工业机甲足以只身应对。COSMO已制定了应急方案，帮助你抵御黑雾的攻击。在建设你的工厂时，你将需要部署必要的防御设施，你的活动越活跃，黑雾将更加频繁地发动猛烈攻击。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用你的防御设施释放“烟火”，驱散黑雾。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/ed94c3312f98d06966c5476e4e39f85b.poster.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/ed94c3312f98d06966c5476e4e39f85b.webm?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/ed94c3312f98d06966c5476e4e39f85b.mp4?t=1765532615\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1366540/extras/388b8e316d7aa2926cc75e11bb8e48f3.avif?t=1765532615\" width=780 height=122 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们是来自中国重庆的柚子猫工作室，从最初的五人开发团队到如今逐渐壮大的队伍（人也不多啦），我们与《戴森球计划》一同前行。出于对科幻的喜爱，我们制作了《戴森球计划》，从建造第一台采矿机到遍布星辰的自动化工厂，希望你们能够享受它带来的乐趣，和我们一样喜欢这款游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >想了解《戴森球计划》的最新资讯吗？关注我们：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B站：戴森球计划制作组</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方微博：@戴森球计划制作组, @GameraGames</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方群：603826927、628570136、949042234</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方bug反馈群：777178167</p>",
